This method will retrieve the rules from a specific Price Table.

## Response body example

```json
{
    "tradePolicyId": "b2c",
    "rules": [{
        "id": 0,
        "context": {
            "categories": {},
            "brands": {
                "2000009": "Whiskas"
            },
            "stockStatuses": null,
            "internalCategories": null,
            "markupRange": null,
            "dateRange": null
        },
        "percentualModifier": 15
    }]
}
```

This method will retrieve all price tables and their rules.

## Response body example

